snippet.title: Car Demolition Clicker - PC Gameplay (Steam)
snippet.description:
This is an idle clicker where you click on cars to destroy them for cash. The cash can be used to upgrade the guns, hover turrets and more. Also on PS4.

Developed by Blue Sunset Games

Steam link: https://store.steampowered.com/app/705740/Car_Demolition_Clicker/
